title: Flights online v 1.0.1.ipa
description:
New international version of the popular app turn your iPhone or iPad into the Arrivals and Departures board for any airport in the world.
This app works great on all iPhone, iPod Touches and iPad with network access.

Flights online is a powerful application for all flights worldwide. 
You can check the status of the flights by flight number, by airport name or city name.

- Easy to search for a specific flight
- Support 20000+ Airports
- Provides information about flight delay and cancellations
